WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
Love is our shared truth.

00:05.000 --> 00:09.000
Peace is our eternal hope.

00:31.000 --> 00:35.000
We have to pray for this war

00:35.000 --> 00:40.000
so that the war can end quickly

00:40.000 --> 00:44.000
and that everyone can live in harmony.

00:44.000 --> 00:49.000
We must not look for peace from conflicts.

00:49.000 --> 00:52.000
We should look for peace from sharing.

00:52.000 --> 00:56.000
We should respect the value of existence,

00:56.000 --> 00:59.000
embrace everyone's space,

00:59.000 --> 01:02.000
and share everyone's achievements.

01:02.000 --> 01:06.000
This is the way we feel about each other.

01:06.000 --> 01:09.000
We, the religious people, work together

01:09.000 --> 01:12.000
to pray for this war

01:12.000 --> 01:15.000
so that this pain does not happen

01:15.000 --> 01:18.000
and we can return to normal quickly.

01:18.000 --> 01:23.000
Only when we find peace can we turn back.

01:23.000 --> 01:26.000
How do we start from the ecosystem?

01:26.000 --> 01:29.000
If the ecosystem has power, this will be solved.

01:29.000 --> 01:31.000
It is impossible without power.

01:31.000 --> 01:33.000
If the ecosystem has power, everyone knows.

01:33.000 --> 01:35.000
We have to live.

01:35.000 --> 01:38.000
We have to protect the Earth.

01:38.000 --> 01:41.000
If we want the Earth, we have to protect everyone.

01:45.000 --> 01:47.000
In this day and age,

01:47.000 --> 01:50.000
when values are mixed,

01:50.000 --> 01:55.000
a lot of people are worried or anxious.

01:55.000 --> 01:59.000
I would like to introduce our former prophet,

01:59.000 --> 02:01.000
President Nelson Nelson.

02:01.000 --> 02:05.000
He used Jesus Christ as an example to encourage us.

02:05.000 --> 02:06.000
He said,

02:06.000 --> 02:08.000
I wish you all

02:08.000 --> 02:11.000
to use good words to persuade each other

02:11.000 --> 02:13.000
to fight and provoke.

02:13.000 --> 02:17.000
Use understanding to replace hostility.

02:17.000 --> 02:21.000
Use peace to replace conflict.

02:21.000 --> 02:25.000
The survivor is Jesus Christ.

02:25.000 --> 02:27.000
He is the head of this church.

02:27.000 --> 02:29.000
We are his servants.

02:29.000 --> 02:34.000
He will help us to become his messengers of peace.

02:34.000 --> 02:38.000
I witness this in the name of Jesus Christ. Amen.

02:42.000 --> 02:44.000
Peace be upon you.

02:44.000 --> 02:46.000
May the Lord's peace be upon you.

02:46.000 --> 02:49.000
In accordance with the will of Jesus Christ,

02:49.000 --> 02:52.000
in accordance with the rules he made for us,

02:52.000 --> 02:55.000
we will naturally attain peace.

02:55.000 --> 02:58.000
Jesus Christ created so many different ethnicities,

02:58.000 --> 03:00.000
different cultures, different ethnic groups.

03:00.000 --> 03:03.000
He did not decide who is superior and who is inferior.

03:03.000 --> 03:07.000
He decided to follow the rules of this world

03:07.000 --> 03:10.000
in accordance with the rules of this world.

03:10.000 --> 03:14.000
In the end, he was regarded as a superior person.

03:14.000 --> 03:16.000
Of course, in this world,

03:16.000 --> 03:19.000
no one can judge that a person is superior to another.

03:19.000 --> 03:22.000
Therefore, there must be a consensus between human beings

03:22.000 --> 03:24.000
so that we can coexist,

03:24.000 --> 03:26.000
live in harmony,

03:26.000 --> 03:28.000
and eventually attain peace.

03:31.000 --> 03:34.000
As religion, especially the Orthodox Church,

03:34.000 --> 03:36.000
says that God is love,

03:36.000 --> 03:38.000
not has emotion,

03:38.000 --> 03:40.000
exists as coexistence,

03:40.000 --> 03:42.000
the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit.

03:42.000 --> 03:44.000
And as God exists,

03:44.000 --> 03:46.000
it's the coexistence that makes existence,

03:46.000 --> 03:48.000
calls us to coexist,

03:48.000 --> 03:50.000
to exist because you exist,

03:50.000 --> 03:52.000
not because of me.

03:52.000 --> 03:55.000
And you are my life, and you are my salvation.

03:55.000 --> 03:59.000
The religious leaders, if we want to be honest,

03:59.000 --> 04:02.000
cannot exercise political power,

04:02.000 --> 04:04.000
cannot have political positions,

04:04.000 --> 04:08.000
because peace is not only we don't fight.

04:08.000 --> 04:11.000
Peace, by that way, is in a prison.

04:11.000 --> 04:13.000
Peace means human rights,

04:13.000 --> 04:15.000
freedom,

04:15.000 --> 04:19.000
at least some freedom and respect

04:19.000 --> 04:21.000
in the human being,

04:21.000 --> 04:23.000
in the human rights.

04:23.000 --> 04:25.000
We must be very honest,

04:25.000 --> 04:27.000
because if we exercise the human rights,

04:27.000 --> 04:29.000
it's a very important thing.

04:33.000 --> 04:35.000
Shalom, shalom means in Hebrew, hello,

04:35.000 --> 04:37.000
it also means greeting,

04:37.000 --> 04:39.000
and it also means peace,

04:39.000 --> 04:43.000
and the way which peace could be attained

04:43.000 --> 04:45.000
is if people would understand

04:45.000 --> 04:49.000
and realize that God is watching over us,

04:49.000 --> 04:51.000
and he cares about us,

04:51.000 --> 04:53.000
and we're all his children,

04:53.000 --> 04:55.000
no matter what is our religion,

04:55.000 --> 04:57.000
and no matter what is our background,

04:57.000 --> 04:59.000
what country we live in,

04:59.000 --> 05:01.000
what language we speak,

05:01.000 --> 05:03.000
everyone are God's children,

05:03.000 --> 05:05.000
and he created us and put us in this world

05:05.000 --> 05:07.000
in order to make the world a better place,

05:07.000 --> 05:09.000
to be rectified, to elevate the world.

05:09.000 --> 05:11.000
And in that spirit,

05:11.000 --> 05:13.000
we all, all human beings,

05:13.000 --> 05:15.000
are equal to that part.

05:15.000 --> 05:17.000
Everyone understands that we,

05:17.000 --> 05:19.000
as long as we understand that we are

05:19.000 --> 05:21.000
creatures created by God

05:21.000 --> 05:23.000
for the purpose of making the world a better place,

05:23.000 --> 05:25.000
we can get along with each other.

05:25.000 --> 05:27.000
There's no room and no place

05:27.000 --> 05:29.000
and no idea for people

05:29.000 --> 05:31.000
to start getting involved

05:31.000 --> 05:33.000
in matters of bloodshed

05:33.000 --> 05:35.000
and in wars and so on.

05:35.000 --> 05:37.000
I would like to extend our wishes

05:37.000 --> 05:39.000
and our hope and prayer

05:39.000 --> 05:41.000
that the world will be

05:41.000 --> 05:43.000
what it's supposed to be,

05:43.000 --> 05:45.000
that the purpose in which it was created

05:45.000 --> 05:47.000
will be fulfilled.

06:05.000 --> 06:07.000
When we live in the human world,

06:07.000 --> 06:09.000
we need to pay special attention

06:09.000 --> 06:11.000
to the harmony between

06:11.000 --> 06:13.000
all beings and all things.

06:13.000 --> 06:15.000
And this kind of harmony

06:15.000 --> 06:17.000
is the eternal truth of the universe.

06:17.000 --> 06:19.000
When we have love in our hearts,

06:19.000 --> 06:21.000
when we think about other things around us,

06:21.000 --> 06:23.000
it also needs to have

06:23.000 --> 06:25.000
a little love and care

06:25.000 --> 06:27.000
that we give to it

06:27.000 --> 06:29.000
and when we give it

06:29.000 --> 06:31.000
special attention,

06:31.000 --> 06:33.000
it also needs to have

06:33.000 --> 06:35.000
a special relationship

06:35.000 --> 06:37.000
that is harmonious with each other.

06:37.000 --> 06:39.000
We need to love each other

06:39.000 --> 06:41.000
with our own hearts.

06:45.000 --> 06:47.000
If there is a war,

06:47.000 --> 06:49.000
it will definitely create a social chaos.

06:49.000 --> 06:51.000
What's important is that

06:51.000 --> 06:53.000
the conflict between a country and a country

06:53.000 --> 06:55.000
and the family

06:55.000 --> 06:57.000
will be destroyed.

06:57.000 --> 06:59.000
Everyone will be separated

06:59.000 --> 07:01.000
from their loved ones

07:01.000 --> 07:03.000
and even those who are alive will die.

07:03.000 --> 07:05.000
So it will be a tragedy.

07:05.000 --> 07:07.000
Last week,

07:07.000 --> 07:09.000
we held a meeting

07:09.000 --> 07:11.000
for the peace of religion

07:11.000 --> 07:13.000
to pray for world peace.

07:13.000 --> 07:15.000
We are also willing

07:15.000 --> 07:17.000
to connect

07:17.000 --> 07:19.000
different religions

07:19.000 --> 07:21.000
and to persuade

07:21.000 --> 07:23.000
different religions

07:23.000 --> 07:25.000
to move towards peace

07:25.000 --> 07:27.000
and to move forward.

07:27.000 --> 07:29.000
When the society is in chaos,

07:29.000 --> 07:31.000
the first religion came out,

07:31.000 --> 07:33.000
the 24th religion,

07:33.000 --> 07:35.000
and it called for

07:35.000 --> 07:37.000
different religions

07:37.000 --> 07:39.000
to pray for peace

07:39.000 --> 07:41.000
in Misha.

07:41.000 --> 07:43.000
In Misha, there is a belief

07:43.000 --> 07:45.000
that we should pray for peace,

07:45.000 --> 07:47.000
for the peace of the Middle East.

07:47.000 --> 07:49.000
Everyone needs to have

07:49.000 --> 07:51.000
this motivation.

07:51.000 --> 07:53.000
Only peace can make us happy.

07:53.000 --> 07:55.000
If there is no peace,

07:55.000 --> 07:57.000
there will be no

07:57.000 --> 07:59.000
happiness.

07:59.000 --> 08:01.000
We call for

08:01.000 --> 08:03.000
different religions

08:03.000 --> 08:05.000
to pursue peace,

08:05.000 --> 08:07.000
to seek peace,

08:07.000 --> 08:09.000
to seek peace.

08:09.000 --> 08:11.000
This is a common feature.

08:11.000 --> 08:13.000
We should all work together

08:13.000 --> 08:15.000
in this direction

08:15.000 --> 08:17.000
to seek peace.

08:17.000 --> 08:19.000
We should all pray

08:19.000 --> 08:21.000
for peace

08:21.000 --> 08:23.000
and seek peace.

08:27.000 --> 08:29.000
You

